[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "He was then for granting a hundred years.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "The conversation now turned upon mr David Hume's style.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "But if you allow that the English language is established, he is wrong.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "My name might originally have been Nicholson, as well as Johnson; but were you to call me Nicholson now, you would call me very absurdly.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "JOHNSON.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Now, Sir, in civilized society, external advantages make us more respected.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Sir, you may analyse this, and say what is there in it?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "But that will avail you nothing, for it is a part of a general system.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Pound saint Paul's Church into atoms, and consider any single atom; it is, to be sure, good for nothing: but, put all these atoms together, and you have saint Paul's Church.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "So it is with human felicity, which is made up of many ingredients, each of which may be shewn to be very insignificant. In civilized society, personal merit will not serve you so much as money will.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Sir, you may make the experiment.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Go into the street, and give one man a lecture on morality, and another a shilling, and see which will respect you most.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Now, Sir, all beyond this is artificial, and is desired in order to obtain a greater degree of respect from our fellow creatures.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Money, to be sure, of itself is of no use; for its only use is to part with it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Why, now, there is stealing; why should it be thought a crime?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000007_000017",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000007_000017.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Yet, Sir, the experience of mankind has discovered stealing to be so very bad a thing, that they make no scruple to hang a man for it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "It was suggested that Kings must be unhappy, because they are deprived of the greatest of all satisfactions, easy and unreserved society. JOHNSON. 'That is an ill founded notion.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Being a King does not exclude a man from such society.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Great Kings have always been social.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "JOHNSON. 'Why, Sir, mankind have found that this cannot be.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "How shall we determine the proportion of intrinsick merit?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "But, Sir, as subordination is very necessary for society, and contensions for superiority very dangerous, mankind, that is to say, all civilized nations, have settled it upon a plain invariable principle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000010_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000010_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "A man is born to hereditary rank; or his being appointed to certain offices, gives him a certain rank.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000010_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000010_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Subordination tends greatly to human happiness.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "I said, I considered distinction of rank to be of so much importance in civilised society, that if I were asked on the same day to dine with the first Duke in England, and with the first man in Britain for genius, I should hesitate which to prefer.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "JOHNSON.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "He took care to guard himself against any possible suspicion that his settled principles of reverence for rank and respect for wealth were at all owing to mean or interested motives; for he asserted his own independence as a literary man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Next morning I found him alone, and have preserved the following fragments of his conversation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "He is totally unfixed in his principles, and wants to puzzle other people.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "I said his principles had been poisoned by a noted infidel writer, but that he was, nevertheless, a benevolent good man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000015_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000015_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "JOHNSON.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000015_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000015_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "'We can have no dependance upon that instinctive, that constitutional goodness which is not founded upon principle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000015_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000015_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "I grant you that such a man may be a very amiable member of society.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000015_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000015_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "I can conceive him placed in such a situation that he is not much tempted to deviate from what is right; and as every man prefers virtue, when there is not some strong incitement to transgress its precepts, I can conceive him doing nothing wrong.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000015_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000015_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Every thing which Hume has advanced against Christianity had passed through my mind long before he wrote. Always remember this, that after a system is well settled upon positive evidence, a few partial objections ought not to shake it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000015_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000015_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "The human mind is so limited, that it cannot take in all the parts of a subject, so that there may be objections raised against any thing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "JOHNSON. 'Why, Sir, the great difficulty of proving miracles should make us very cautious in believing them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "But let us consider; although GOD has made Nature to operate by certain fixed laws, yet it is not unreasonable to think that he may suspend those laws, in order to establish a system highly advantageous to mankind.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000017_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000017_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Now the Christian religion is a most beneficial system, as it gives us light and certainty where we were before in darkness and doubt.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000017_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000017_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "The miracles which prove it are attested by men who had no interest in deceiving us; but who, on the contrary, were told that they should suffer persecution, and did actually lay down their lives in confirmation of the truth of the facts which they asserted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000017_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000017_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Indeed, for some centuries the heathens did not pretend to deny the miracles; but said they were performed by the aid of evil spirits.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000017_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000017_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "This is a circumstance of great weight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "'Sir, I love the acquaintance of young people; because, in the first place, I don't like to think myself growing old.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "My judgement, to be sure, was not so good; but I had all the facts.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000021_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000021_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "It is pleasing to consider that the old gentleman's gloomy prophecy as to the irksomeness of books to men of an advanced age, which is too often fulfilled, was so far from being verified in Johnson, that his ardour for literature never failed, and his last writings had more ease and vivacity than any of his earlier productions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "Against melancholy he recommended constant occupation of mind, a great deal of exercise, moderation in eating and drinking, and especially to shun drinking at night.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "He observed, that labouring men who work hard, and live sparingly, are seldom or never troubled with low spirits.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2096_136868_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2096/136868/2096_136868_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "He again insisted on the duty of maintaining subordination of rank. 'Sir, I would no more deprive a nobleman of his respect, than of his money.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
