        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2096",
        "content": "'tis true I am paid for doing it; but so are you, Sir: and I am sorry to say it, paid better than I am, for doing something not so necessary.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
